name: Category
description: category, type or other form of classification

name: Geography
description: geographical boundary, extent, zone or other area with a geometry and a point

name: Legal instrument
description: legal text such as an order, licence, permit, title, contract, agreement, or notice

name: Organisation
description: department, agency, body, company, group, or association of people

name: Pipeline
description: configuration needed by the data pipeline

name: Policy
description: principle or protocol to guide decisions and achieve an outcome

name: Specification
description: description, configuration, requirements, and other metadata needed by the service

name: Timetable
description: times when events are intended to take place
